Package org.pepstock.charba.client.plugins

Class AbstractBasePlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.plugins.AbstractBasePlugin
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SmartPlugin, WrapperPlugin
    public abstract class AbstractBasePlugin
extends NativeObjectContainer
    Base plugin class implementation.
    It represents the instance to store in CHART.JS configuration.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero

      • invokeUninstall

        abstract void invokeUninstall​(IsChart chart)
        Called after chart is destroyed on all plugins that were installed for that chart.
        This hook is also invoked for disabled plugins (options equals to false).
        Parameters:
        chart - chart instance
